{"tid":421413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人嘅主子屙屎有血","createTime":"2017-10-02T08:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T08:43:45.000Z","uid":110429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9d73e01f644d7a23027ba5352d5b913b14b25be0","tid":421413,"uid":110429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:36:17.000Z","msg":"我隻主子3個月大，前日朝早同今日下晝屙屎帶血之前未試過，好擔心，但佢又食得玩得，有冇人嘅主子都試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住過多幾日仲係咁就帶佢睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bf9d9ead891a1fc6bf0316fa9925e1c40c5ec2","tid":421413,"uid":110429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f3844cb0068250f367b6aa3678da683e67f735e","tid":421413,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:40:29.000Z","msg":"隻貓成日有鮮血，但佢天生腸粗<br />\n醫生話應該係屎粗整損屎眼"},{"pid":"ebdf78998af7767cd8f26735aed9ac58a6cc98f5","tid":421413,"uid":110429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻貓成日有鮮血，但佢天生腸粗<br />\n醫生話應該係屎粗整損屎眼</blockquote><br />\n我個隻都係痴住啲鮮血，通常係第一舊先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屎眼都有小小跡，你會唔會幫佢抆屎"}]}